            <div class="service-card">
              <div class="service-icon">üè≠</div>
              <h3>Industrial Manufacturing</h3>
              <p>Heavy-duty epoxy systems designed for Middletown's manufacturing facilities, providing chemical resistance and durability for industrial operations.</p>
              <ul>
                <li>Chemical-resistant industrial coatings</li>
                <li>Heavy machinery load capacity</li>
                <li>Anti-slip safety surfaces</li>
                <li>Fast-cure minimal downtime options</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="service-card">
