                <li>Basement moisture control</li>
                <li>Workshop and hobby area coatings</li>
                <li>Custom color and design options</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Local Expertise -->
      <section class="local-expertise">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="content-columns">
            <div class="content-column">
              <h2>Why Choose Our Middletown Epoxy Services?</h2>
              
              <h3>Butler County Industrial Knowledge</h3>
              <p>
                Middletown's rich manufacturing heritage spans from steel production to modern advanced 
                manufacturing. Our team understands the specific demands of industrial environments, 
                from chemical resistance requirements to load-bearing specifications that Butler County's 
                diverse industrial facilities require.
              </p>
              
              <h3>Great Miami River Valley Experience</h3>
              <p>
                Located in the Great Miami River valley, Middletown faces unique environmental challenges 
                including humidity, potential flooding, and soil conditions that affect concrete performance. 
                Our epoxy systems are specifically designed to handle these regional conditions while 
                providing long-term durability.
              </p>
              
              <h3>Academic and Community Understanding</h3>
              <p>
