                services that meet the needs of educational facilities, student housing, and family homes. 
                Our solutions balance performance requirements with aesthetic considerations for community spaces.
              </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="content-column">
              <h3>Featured Middletown Projects</h3>
              
              <div class="project-highlight">
                <h4>Advanced Manufacturing Facility</h4>
                <p>
                  <strong>Challenge:</strong> 75,000 sq ft automotive parts manufacturing plant requiring 
                  chemical-resistant flooring that could handle hydraulic fluids, cutting oils, and 
                  heavy equipment traffic while meeting automotive industry cleanliness standards.
                </p>
                <p>
                  <strong>Solution:</strong> Multi-zone epoxy system with specialized chemical-resistant 
                  topcoats in production areas, high-build systems for heavy traffic zones, and 
                  ESD-compliant coatings for quality control areas.
                </p>
                <p>
                  <strong>Result:</strong> "Exceptional performance under demanding production conditions. 
                  The floor system has maintained its integrity and appearance through three years of 
                  continuous automotive manufacturing operations." - Plant Manager, Advanced Manufacturing
                </p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="project-highlight">
                <h4>Historic Downtown Mixed-Use Development</h4>
                <p>
