                  housing retail space, offices, and residential units requiring modern flooring that 
                  respected the building's historic character.
                </p>
                <p>
                  <strong>Solution:</strong> Custom-tinted epoxy systems with period-appropriate earth 
                  tones and subtle texture patterns that complemented the building's brick and timber 
                  architecture while providing modern durability.
                </p>
                <p>
                  <strong>Result:</strong> Perfect integration of historical preservation requirements 
                  with contemporary performance needs, enhancing the building's appeal to tenants and visitors.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
